Known commands:
- pnpm install
- pnpm test
- pnpm -r typecheck
- pnpm --filter @compliance-ai/web build
- pnpm smoke:demo
- pnpm test to validate agents, cognition, and web behavior.
- pnpm -r typecheck to validate the monorepo TypeScript surface.
- pnpm --filter @compliance-ai/web build before any hosted demo.
- pnpm smoke:demo against the deployed or local app.

[handoff]
- Load agent passport id=load_agent_passport
- Follow replay prompt id=follow_replay_prompt after=load_agent_passport
- Regenerate proof chain after changes id=agent_refresh_proof after=follow_replay_prompt

